snippet.title: Need for Speed Unbound - Risk & Reward Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
To get to the top, you gotta take risks. Choose how and when to put it all on the line, pulling huge drifts on the street, outdriving the cops, or placing side bets with your own earnings against rival racers. Time is money, so find the fastest way to earn enough cash to enter the weekly qualifiers and make it to Lakeshore’s ultimate race, The Grand.
Start at the bottom and race to the top in Need for Speed™ Unbound, coming to PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S and PC on December 2, 2022.
Pre-order now to get 3 days early access and exclusive Need For Speed Unbound items: http://x.ea.com/74626 

Find out more about Need for Speed Unbound: http://x.ea.com/74625
